  "display_name": "Fibromyalgia and Chronic Fatigue Syndrome Research",
  "description": "This cluster of papers focuses on the diagnosis, management, and understanding of fibromyalgia syndrome, including its overlap with chronic fatigue syndrome. It covers topics such as pain processing, central sensitization, diagnostic criteria, treatment approaches, neurobiology, psychological factors, and epidemiology.",
